speedy-socials
==============

This project incorporates source code (and structural inspiration) from
third-party projects. The original sources were absorbed into the tree
during the Phase 0 transition and have since been re-implemented in
Tiger Style under `src/protocols/`. The legacy absorbed trees were
retired on 2026-05-14 (Phase 8). The attributions below remain because
the original structure and design informed the rewrite.

